                                    TrueCar Certified Dealer guarantees that you will receive at least a certain, stated minimum
                                    savings amount off the base Manufacturer's Suggested Retail Price ("MSRP"). Including any
                                    vehicle-specific manufacturer incentives currently available. Guaranteed Savings only
                                    applies to in-stock vehicles at the selected TrueCar Certified Dealers. Incentives subject
                                    to certain terms, conditions and restrictions, see your TrueCar Certified Dealer for
                                    details.









